word_mean_info__list.difference: 语气最强，指保持永久不变，没有中断的行为，永无止境地持续下去。有时用于贬义，指令人厌烦之事。
指总是处于相同的情况和地位，可长期持续下去，永久不变。
系日常用词，指无尽无休。
语气较庄重，有时可与eternal换用，侧重持续不尽，或指开始后一直进行下去。
语体较庄重，侧重指永远存在，无始无终。

bilingual.target: 孩子的好奇心是无穷无尽的。
旅行带给了我们无尽的乐趣。
旅行给了她无尽的快感。
旅行给了他们无尽的享乐。

bilingual.source: He tortures his mind with endless doubts.
bilingual.target: 他用无尽的疑虑折磨自己的心灵。

bilingual.source: The desert is covered with endless sands.
bilingual.target: 沙漠被无尽的沙子覆盖。
他的成功带给了他无尽的幸福快乐。

bilingual.source: The prairie is an endless expanse of grass.
bilingual.target: 草原是一片无尽的草地。

bilingual.source: He faced endless challenges but never gave up.
bilingual.target: 他面对无尽的挑战，但从未放弃。

bilingual.source: The ocean's beauty is endless and mesmerizing.
bilingual.target: 海洋的美丽是无尽的，令人着迷。

list.abstract: 为了最大限度地提高性能和车辆的潜力，Endless 集团有许多项目。分为2个组 Endless 项目组和Endless 营销。Endless 的重点项目作为一个刹车片开发商和制造商的角色。Endless 的进展的重点是销售和Endless 的热情和产品营销，以及维护和racecars销售。从赛车取得的经验，然后制定并反馈到街道释放我们的产品。Endless 的集团已在全球网络渠道和使用的座右铭钬淭他将获胜。

yingyinNormal.en: That's long term memory. An endless swarm of corridors and shelves. I read about it in the manuals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是长期记忆，无尽的走廊和记忆架子，我在手册里读到过。

yingyinNormal.en: Look around, man-cub. I got everything. I have plentiful food, endless treasure, command vast legions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你都看到了，人孩，我什么都有了，我有充足的食物，无尽的财富，甚至还能指挥千军万马。

yingyinNormal.en: It will set you on a path from which there is no return, an endless cycle of killing us and them till there is nothing left.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这会让你走上一条不归路的，一条无尽的杀戮之路，直到我们都所剩无几。

yingyinNormal.en: You memorized conjugations for an endless list of verbs.
Good for you. I just had a seemingly endless dinner with your mom. Oh, yeah? That's nice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就好，我刚跟你妈吃了一顿没完没了的晚餐。是吗？那不错啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I remember the rest of that day as an endless drill of police and photographers and tabloid reporters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还记得那天余下的时间充斥着络绎不绝的警察摄影师和小报记者。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm upset for you. I mean, having sex with an endless line of beautiful women must be very unfulfilling for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是为了你，不断跟美女追求性爱，一定很空虚。

yingyinNormal.en: For far too long, Lily's friends just haven't challenged her. It's been this endless procession of paste-eating, toilet-missing shoe-losers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太久以来莉莉的朋友们都无法挑战她，一直以来她的朋友都是吃胶水，尿不进马桶，找不到鞋子的傻孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: Take a camel trek, meet the wildlife, or just gaze out at the endless expanse of sands. This is a place so quiet, you can hear your own heart beat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 骑上骆驼、观赏野生动植物，或者纯粹凝视无际的沙漠。沙漠上万籁俱寂，您甚至可以听到自己的心跳声。

yingyinNormal.en: Marina Bay shines like something from a science fiction blockbuster, while Gardens by the Bay shows the endless possibilities of mankind's flowering imagination.
yingyinNormal.zh: 滨海湾金沙就像科幻小说的建筑一样，触目耀眼，而滨海湾花园则展现了人类对花卉想象的无限可能性。

yingyinNormal.en: You know? I'm sitting there. I got that 800 thread count sheets. I got the endless minibar snacks. You got the fancy oatmeal soaps, plush robes and all I can do is sit there and think about how quiet it is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就坐在那儿，虽然那里有八百针的高质量床单，迷你冰箱里也有吃不完的小吃，还有高级的燕麦香皂和长毛绒睡袍，而我就只坐在那儿，默默地想着，太安静了。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 是日常用词，指数量上无线的或事情无休止的。
语体较庄重，侧重指永远存在，无始无终。
语气较庄重，有时可与 eternal 换用，侧重持续不尽，或指开始后一直进行下去。
